{"word":"εὐλογία","slug":"εὐλογία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>εὐλογία, ας, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εὐλογέω\">εὐλογέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘expression of high commendation’, <b>praise <a href='B:660 3:10'>Js 3:10</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vs.\">vs.</a> 9); <b><a href='B:730 5:12'>Rv 5:12f</a>; <a href='B:730 7:12'>7:12</a>.</b> In pejorative sense<b> flattery <a href='B:520 16:18'>Ro 16:18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘bestowal of favor’, <b>blessing, gift <a href='B:520 15:29'>Ro 15:29</a>; <a href='B:560 1:3'>Eph 1:3</a>; <a href='B:650 6:7'>Hb 6:7</a>; <a href='B:650 12:17'>12:17</a>; <a href='B:670 3:9'>1 Pt 3:9</a>;</b> <el>τὀ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ποτήριον\">ποτήριον</a> τῆς εὐλογίας</el> the cup filled with blessing<b> <a href='B:530 10:16'>1 Cor 10:16</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:εὐλογητός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:εὐμετάδοτος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}